'''UDON''', also known as '''UdonCrew''' and '''UDON Entertainment''', is an [[Wikipedia:Artist collective|Art collective]]<ref name="AboutUDON">{{DeviantArt|username=UdonCrew|url=udoncrew/aboutus|name=UDON|text=About UdonCrew}}</ref> commissioned to color the comic "[[Ghosts of Hoth]]" and illustrated the cover for ''[[Star Wars Tales 17]]''.

Members include [[Roberto Campus]], who did the cover of [[Star Wars Insider 87]];<ref name="Insider87">{{DeviantArt|username=UdonCrew|url=udoncrew/art/Jedi-Hunted-45157210|name=UDON|text=Jedi Hunted by UdonCrew|date=2006-12-23}}</ref> [[Eric Vedder]], who did linework for artwork accompanying [[Star Wars Insider]] articles;<ref name="TrooperDown">{{DeviantArt|username=UdonCrew|url=udoncrew/art/Trooper-Down-46067996|name=UDON|text=Trooper Down|date=2007-01-06}}</ref> [[Joe Ng]] and [[Kevin Yan]], who contributed linework and paints respectively for some artwork in [[The Force Unleashed Campaign Guide]];<ref name="Felucian">{{DeviantArt|username=UdonCrew|url=udoncrew/art/Star-Wars-Felucian-Shaman-98018471|name=UDON|text=Star Wars&ndash; Felucian Shaman|date=2008-09-15}}</ref> [[Saejin Oh]], who worked on the [[Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide]];<ref name="KOTORraces">{{DeviantArt|username=UdonCrew|url=udoncrew/art/KoTOR-Races-97361393|name=UDON|text=KOTOR&ndash; Races|date=2008-09-08}}</ref> and [[Alvin Lee]] and [[Arnold Tsang]], who respectively did the lines and colors for the cover of [[Dark Horse Comics]]' seventeenth issue of [[Star Wars Tales]].<ref name="SWT">{{DeviantArt|username=UdonCrew|url=udoncrew/art/Star-Wars-Tales-45994578|name=UDON|text=Star Wars Tales|date=2007-01-05}}</ref>

